1
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:14,120
I'm asking you.

2
00:00:14,120 --> 00:00:15,000
Say something.

3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:15,920
Stop covering it up.

4
00:00:15,920 --> 00:00:16,680
Yeah, yeah.

5
00:00:16,680 --> 00:00:17,800
Everything you said is right.

6
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:24,480
Strategist.

7
00:00:25,040 --> 00:00:26,120
Miss Aqin seems a bit unhappy.

8
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:26,760
I don't know why.

9
00:00:26,880 --> 00:00:27,880
I'm the one who's unhappy.

10
00:00:28,880 --> 00:00:29,640
Strategist, what happened to you?

11
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:31,160
Aqin punched me.

12
00:00:31,560 --> 00:00:32,160
Why?

13
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:34,280
Just now, while you weren't looking...

14
00:00:34,720 --> 00:00:35,960
I touched her hand.

15
00:00:36,160 --> 00:00:36,800
Serves you right.

16
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:37,480
That's my wife.

17
00:00:37,480 --> 00:00:38,360
I haven't even touched her yet.

18
00:00:38,360 --> 00:00:39,000
And you touched her.

19
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:39,640
Keep it down.

20
00:00:40,760 --> 00:00:41,680
I was testing her.

21
00:00:41,680 --> 00:00:42,640
Testing?

22
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:44,880
She knows martial arts.

23
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:46,560
Really?

24
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:48,440
The calluses on her hands...

25
00:00:48,680 --> 00:00:50,880
take at least ten years of weapon training to form.

26
00:00:51,360 --> 00:00:52,120
That can't be.

27
00:00:52,440 --> 00:00:53,400
Look at this injury of mine.

28
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:55,360
The Lord has punched me before too.

29
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:57,240
Her strength is no different from the Lord's.

30
00:00:58,040 --> 00:00:59,920
The Lord is the top general of our Wei Kingdom.

31
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:02,200
So Aqin's skills...

32
00:01:02,480 --> 00:01:03,400
are unfathomable.

33
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:04,680
I'll make her leave now.

34
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:07,640
Don't you know your own skill level?

35
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:09,920
Can you and Wei Qiao together beat her?

36
00:01:10,240 --> 00:01:11,000
We have you, don't we?

37
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,160
I'm good at shouting matches.

38
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:14,040
We have to tell Wei Qiao about this.

39
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:15,800
Qiao.

40
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:16,280
Come here.

41
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:19,040
What's wrong?

42
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:22,480
Miss Aqin is not to be trifled with.

43
00:01:22,800 --> 00:01:23,360
You have to be on your guard.

44
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,680
She is very likely a spy from Daye Kingdom.

45
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:26,440
A spy?

46
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,000
Then get rid of her quickly.

47
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:29,480
If we could handle her...

48
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,040
we would have done it already.

49
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:30,920
We've been discussing it for ages here.

50
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:31,320
Exactly.

51
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:33,440
Why are you here?

52
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,280
You guys told me to come over.

53
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:36,680
If we tell you to come, you just come?

54
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,640
If you're here, who's driving the carriage?

55
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,240
The carriage is moving on its own.

56
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:40,640
That's fine, that's fine.

57
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:47,240
What happened?

58
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:48,800
What happened?

59
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,040
How did we hit someone?

60
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:53,880
Must be a staged accident.

61
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,560
That's Qiao's full responsibility.

62
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:57,080
I wasn't driving.

63
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:58,640
This carriage belongs to the three of you.

64
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,840
Carry him to the roadside.

65
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:20,240
Move it.

66
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,120
Don't move.

67
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:25,160
I want to save her.

68
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,120
Then hurry up and save her.

69
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:28,360
Artificial respiration.

70
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:28,880
I'll go first.

71
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,880
This is a blind spot in my knowledge.

72
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:35,680
I don't know how either.

73
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,600
Qiao, come on.

74
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:42,760
Help me out.

75
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:47,120
Help me move her.

76
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:49,560
Come, come.

77
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:56,360
Get lost.

78
00:02:58,320 --> 00:02:58,920
Wei Long.

79
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:01,360
Are you sure you're just going to watch?

80
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,440
It's good enough that I can even watch right now.

81
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,200
Come on.

82
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,280
Come on.

83
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:10,400
Come on.

84
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,440
Miss, you're awake.

85
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,360
You scared her.

86
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:24,120
Miss.

87
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:27,520
I'm sorry.

88
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:31,720
It's okay.

89
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:32,920
Miss.

90
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:34,120
We are all good people.

91
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,760
Stop talking.

92
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:37,240
Miss.

93
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:39,200
Although this man is ugly,

94
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,800
but... but we really are good people.

95
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,120
May I ask, Miss,

96
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,520
what is your name?

97
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:48,520
Where do you live?

98
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:49,800
How old are you?

99
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:55,160
What?

100
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:57,640
You don't remember anything?

101
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,200
No... then what do you remember?

102
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,240
Big Brother,

103
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,600
you have no self-awareness at all.

104
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,480
Your aura might be too strong.

105
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,760
Normal people can't handle it.

106
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,200
I...

107
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:19,160
Pardon me.

108
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:30,680
The pulse condition is very chaotic

109
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:33,880
Soul Departure Syndrome

110
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,520
She must have suffered some severe trauma

111
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:38,120
Don't you know what trauma she suffered?

112
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:41,400
Hey, what are you doing?

113
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:44,280
Didn't you say she has Soul Departure Syndrome?

114
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,440
Give her a scare

115
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:47,000
Maybe her soul will come back

116
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:47,560
No

117
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,440
You can scare her, but you...

118
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:49,080
You...

119
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:49,520
Move...

120
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:50,680
You... this...

121
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,880
Why are you holding a sword?

122
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:52,560
Wei Long

123
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,520
Control your people

124
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:57,840
It's getting foggy

125
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,040
It's okay

126
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:01,720
Don't be afraid

127
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:02,560
I'm here

128
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,240
You rest for a while

129
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,520
About the fact that Aqin knows martial arts

130
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:14,760
She didn't hide it herself

131
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:17,720
It shows she isn't a spy

132
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,360
Of course I'm not a spy

133
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,320
The young lady is here

134
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,720
But that young lady...

135
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:24,000
You suspect that young lady too, don't you?

136
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,720
Just now when the Strategist checked her pulse...

137
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:27,840
Her hand...

138
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:29,200
Seemed like she has practiced Internal Martial Arts

139
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:31,280
Her martial arts skills are not below mine

140
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:34,560
Your martial arts skills are above ours

141
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,640
And that young lady's skills are above yours

142
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:38,200
The Strategist can't help

143
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,120
And Wei Qiao is useless

144
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,600
We are at a disadvantage

145
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:42,760
I'm still here

146
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:52,840
Found it

147
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:53,760
Found it

148
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,600
Found the way?

149
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,440
No

150
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,800
I found this herb

151
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,600
This herb

152
00:05:58,760 --> 00:05:59,520
Specifically treats headaches

153
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,320
No need to massage

154
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,160
No need to massage

155
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:09,560
Is my massage bad?

156
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,040
That's not it

157
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,520
Doesn't everyone like this?

158
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,080
Like what?

159
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:19,320
Like them

160
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:20,520
Are you still hot?

161
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:21,880
Mr. Yuwen

162
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,040
If you are tired

163
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,440
Come up and sit for a while

164
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,840
Okay, okay, okay

165
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:27,360
That's not necessary

166
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:29,120
Just be yourself

167
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:34,240
Why are you so good to me?

168
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,160
I told you already

169
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,920
If we don't get married

170
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,840
My father will have to go for military service

171
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,200
He'll have to go to the battlefield

172
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:42,680
Just because of this?

173
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,720
I'll go patrol around again

174
00:06:58,960 --> 00:06:59,840
What's wrong with him?

175
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:01,440
Who cares about him

176
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:05,040
The fog has lifted

177
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,000
Still not leaving?

178
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:31,840
This is the Daye Kingdom's reconnaissance method

179
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:34,280
Similar to Knot records

180
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:36,200
Each knot represents a different meaning

181
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,520
So that means

182
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:39,960
Between Aqin and that young lady

183
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:41,400
One of them is a spy

184
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:48,880
I can guarantee

185
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,280
That young lady never got off the carriage

186
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,480
Isn't this simple?

187
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,880
She tied the knotted rope on you

188
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:54,280
When you went to pick herbs

189
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:55,320
It fell on the ground

190
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,880
Without anyone knowing

191
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:03,840
It's Knockout smoke. Hold your breath

192
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:05,080
Snot?

193
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:06,280
Hold your breath

194
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:11,120
Miss

195
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,320
Hold your breath

196
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,240
Watch out

197
00:08:38,560 --> 00:08:39,000
Don't move
